 Copyright (c) Microsoft Corporation. All Rights Reserved.  
==============================================================================  
  
EXEC mdm.[udpCreateHistoryViews] 27, 1, 19, NULL, 'TEST1';  
EXEC mdm.[udpCreateHistoryViews] 27, 2, 19, NULL, 'TEST2';  
